Carefully fold back cover and stir beans and apples; recover. Continue cooking on high power for 2-3 minutes. After cooking, let stand in microwave 1-2 minutes. Carefully remove tray from microwave. Carefully remove cover. Conventional Oven: Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Do not exceed 350 degrees F. Remove tray from outer carton. Cut plastic film to vent. Put tray on cookie sheet and place in oven. Cook 30-35 minutes. Carefully remove cookie sheet from oven. Let stand on cookie sheet for 1-2 minutes. Carefully remove cover.
